Prerequisite
===============
	$ sudo pacman -S fcitx5-chinese-addons extra-cmake-modules boost


Description
==============
Dayi (http://www.dayi.com) table for fcitx5


How to install
==============
    $ mkdir build
    $ cd build
    $ wget https://raw.githubusercontent.com/bruce-awareit/fcitx5-table-dayi3/main/PKGBUILD
    $ makepkg
    $ sudo pacman -U fcitx5-table-dayi3-$(pkgver)-$(pkgrel)-$(arch)-pkg.tar.xz
    $ fcitx5-configtool
